data.description: WELCOME TO YOUR DREAM 5bd/3-FULL bth FULLY FURNISHED STR-FRIENDLY home nestled in a DESIRABLE community w/ amenities like lakes, beaches, tennis courts, & more! Conveniently located near major highways, enjoy seamless commutes & access to shopping centers. Explore Pocono attractions like Kalahari, Camelback, & Mt Airy Casino. The LARGE front porch leads to an open layout w/ exquisite hardwood floors in the Living, Dining, & STUNNING Eat-In Kitchen w/ SS appliances. SPA ROOM features a year-round HOT TUB, ensuring endless entertainment. 2bds on this floor, including the Primary w/ a PRIVATE bath. 2nd floor has 3bds, one w/ a jack&jill bath. The FENCED-IN SPACIOUS YARD boasts a wrap-around deck, & storage shed. Home is also complete w/ energy-efficient mini splits throughout. Whether you're seeking a permanent residence, a vacation getaway, or a smart investment opportunity, this home is tailor-made to meet all your needs! Don't miss the chance to call this enchanting home your own.
